Tiny House Nation - Season 4, Episode 14




230 Sq. Ft. "Smart House"

Kyle and Jennifer are about as tech savy as it gets. They love the contemporary look and have asked John and Zack to build them a tiny house that's completely modern and tricked out with smart gadgets. Now Zack just has to figure out how to get everything connected and working without crossing any wires.




Original Air Date: 02-Jul-2016
